#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:14
msgid "Creates a sub-view into the screen."
msgstr "创建一个子视图到在屏幕中。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:19
msgid ""
"A Viewport creates a different view into the screen, or a sub-view inside"
" another viewport. Children 2D Nodes will display on it, and children "
"Camera 3D nodes will render on it too."
msgstr ""
"``Viewport`` 会在屏幕中创建一个不同的视图，或在另一个 ``Viewport`` "
"中创建一个子视图。子级2D节点将显示在其上，子级相机、3D节点也将在其上进行渲染。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:21
msgid ""
"Optionally, a viewport can have its own 2D or 3D world, so they don't "
"share what they draw with other viewports."
msgstr "可选地，一个视图对象可以具有自己的2D或3D世界，因此它们不与其他视图对象，共享其绘制的内容。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:23
msgid ""
"If a viewport is a child of a :ref:`ViewportContainer "
"<class_ViewportContainer>`, it will automatically take up its size, "
"otherwise it must be set manually."
msgstr ""
"如果一个视图对象是 :ref:`ViewportContainer <class_ViewportContainer>` "
"的子级，它将自动占用其大小，否则必须手动设置。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:25
msgid ""
"Viewports can also choose to be audio listeners, so they generate "
"positional audio depending on a 2D or 3D camera child of it."
msgstr "视图对象还可以选择成为音频侦听器，因此它们将根据它的一个2D或3D相机子级，生成位置音频。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:27
msgid ""
"Also, viewports can be assigned to different screens in case the devices "
"have multiple screens."
msgstr "此外，如果设备具有多个屏幕，则可以将视图对象，分配给不同的屏幕。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:29
msgid ""
"Finally, viewports can also behave as render targets, in which case they "
"will not be visible unless the associated texture is used to draw."
msgstr "最后，视图对象还可以充当渲染目标，在这种情况下，除非使用关联的纹理进行绘制，否则它们将不可见。"

