#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:184
msgid "**UPDATE_DISABLED** = **0** --- Do not update the render target."
msgstr "**UPDATE_DISABLED** = **0** —— 不要更新渲染目标。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:186
msgid ""
"**UPDATE_ONCE** = **1** --- Update the render target once, then switch to"
" :ref:`UPDATE_DISABLED <class_Viewport_constant_UPDATE_DISABLED>`."
msgstr ""
"**UPDATE_ONCE** = **1** —— 更新渲染目标一次，然后切换到 :ref:`UPDATE_DISABLED "
"<class_Viewport_constant_UPDATE_DISABLED>`。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:188
msgid ""
"**UPDATE_WHEN_VISIBLE** = **2** --- Update the render target only when it"
" is visible. This is the default value."
msgstr "**UPDATE_WHEN_VISIBLE** = **2** —— 仅在渲染目标可见时更新它。这是默认值。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_viewport.rst:190
msgid "**UPDATE_ALWAYS** = **3** --- Always update the render target."
msgstr "**UPDATE_ALWAYS** = **3** —— 始终更新渲染目标。"

